'Call PictureSnapConvert(Int(1), ixmin!, iymin!, CSng(0#), xmin!, ymin!, zmin!, fractionx!, fractiony!)
'If ierror Then Exit Sub
'Call PictureSnapConvert(Int(1), ixmax!, iymax!, CSng(0#), xmax!, ymax!, zmax!, fractionx!, fractiony!)
'If ierror Then Exit Sub

